        'pageid' => 69258841,
        'title' => 'Amborobe',
        'feed' => 'Amborobe is a rural municipality in Madagascar. It belongs to the district of Vohipeno, which is a part of the region of Fitovinany. The population of the municipality was 4,586 in 2018.\nThis municipality is situated alongside National Road 12 North of Vohipeno.\n\n\n== References ==\nLoi 2015 - Creation de la Commune',
