        'feed' => 'Phytoecia cinerascens is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was first described by Kraatz in 1882. It is known from Kazakhstan, Turkmenistan, Kyrgyzstan, Afghanistan, Tajikistan, and Uzbekistan.\n\n\n== References ==',
