        'title' => 'Florida\'s 31st House of Representatives district',
        'feed' => 'Florida\'s 31st House of Representatives district elects one member of the Florida House of Representatives. Currently encompassing part of Brevard county, its current representative is Republican Tyler Sirois.\n\n\n== Representatives from 1967 to the present ==\n\n\n== See also ==\nList of members of the Florida House of Representatives from Brevard County, Florida\n\n\n== References ==',
