        'feed' => 'The 1967 Australia Cup was the sixth season of the Australia Cup, which was the main national association football knockout cup competition in Australia. Sixteen clubs from around Australia qualified to enter the competition.\n\n\n== Teams ==\n\n\n== Bracket ==\n\n\n== Round of 16 ==\n\n\n=== Western Division ===\n\n\n=== Eastern Division ===\n\n\n== Quarter-finals ==\n\n\n== Semi-finals ==\n\n\n== Final ==\n\n\n== References ==',
