        'feed' => 'Doctor Emeritus (Russian:Заслуженный Врач) was the honorary title granted to distinguished physicians by the Presidium of the Supreme Soviet Council of the Union\'s Republic based on a proposal from the Ministry of Health.\n\n\n== References ==',
