        'pageid' => 47595341,
        'title' => 'Cuckold (film)',
        'feed' => 'Cuckold is a 2015 South African drama film directed by Charlie Vundla. It was screened in the Contemporary World Cinema section of the 2015 Toronto International Film Festival. It was also screened at the Pan African Film Festival, in its celebration of Black History Month.\n\n\n== Cast ==\nTerry Pheto as Laura\nLouis Roux as Jon\nCharlie Vundla as Smanga\n\n\n== References ==\n\n\n== External links ==\nCuckold at IMDb',
