        'pageid' => 19032555,
        'title' => 'Nieciesławice',
        'feed' => 'Nieciesławice [ɲɛt͡ɕɛswaˈvit͡sɛ] is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Tuczępy, within Busko County, Świętokrzyskie Voivodeship, in south-central Poland. It lies approximately 3 km (2 mi) south-east of Tuczępy, 22 km (14 mi) east of Busko-Zdrój, and 51 km (32 mi) south-east of the regional capital Kielce.\n\n\n== References ==',
